content:
Old notes may refer to one of the following items:

  • Old notes (Dragon Slayer II), notes written by Zorgoth on his experiments on dragons found during Dragon Slayer II
  • Old notes (A Taste of Hope), notes in Serafina's home that you must obtain for Safalaan during A Taste of Hope.
  • Old notes (The Forsaken Tower), used in The Forsaken Tower to help you identify the cleansing fluid.
  • Old notes (Karuulm Slayer Dungeon), notes written by Karuulm on his experiments on Wyrms, Drakes and Hydras.

It may also refer to items named Old note:

  • Old note (Sins of the Father), notes on the Blisterwood Tree written by Sentinel Bloodmyre.
  • Old note (Secluded Chapel), found in the Secluded Chapel.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.

'''Old notes''' may refer to one of the following items:

* [[Old notes (Dragon Slayer II)]], notes written by [[Zorgoth]] on his experiments on dragons found during [[Dragon Slayer II]]
* [[Old notes (A Taste of Hope)]], notes in [[Serafina]]'s home that you must obtain for [[Safalaan]] during [[A Taste of Hope]].
* [[Old notes (The Forsaken Tower)]], used in [[The Forsaken Tower]] to help you identify the cleansing fluid.
* [[Old notes (Karuulm Slayer Dungeon)]], notes written by [[Karuulm]] on his experiments on [[Wyrm]]s, [[Drake]]s and [[Hydra]]s.

It may also refer to items named '''Old note''':
* [[Old note (Sins of the Father)]], notes on the [[Blisterwood Tree]] written by Sentinel Bloodmyre.
* [[Old note (Secluded Chapel)]], found in the [[Secluded Chapel]].
